507dd5b3-3529-4eb8-b6c0-f36490cf0871.title: <player>
507dd5b3-3529-4eb8-b6c0-f36490cf0871.text: Hi. Interesting building you have here. What's it for?

38f98a4d-8084-49cd-a486-177769bf2592.title: Effigy
38f98a4d-8084-49cd-a486-177769bf2592.text:
You like it? It's simply fabulous, isn't it? A real marvel
of modern design, made just for my fellow alchemists
and me!

c43ff895-0082-4d86-a045-e0b43ef74d99.title: <player>
c43ff895-0082-4d86-a045-e0b43ef74d99.text:
I see some builders over there. So I assume it's not yet
finished.

bcab6b8e-ff80-4473-aabb-1e5d1b10d459.title: Effigy
bcab6b8e-ff80-4473-aabb-1e5d1b10d459.text:
What a keen eye you have! But imagine this: a
gargantuan cylinder of expert design, incorporating an
inventive inner spiral walkway to multiple planes of
wondrous inhabitance!

b29e7213-65e1-42e6-b07d-ad5e420dcc46.title: Effigy
b29e7213-65e1-42e6-b07d-ad5e420dcc46.text:
Oh, no, no, no, no. It's going to have a use that will
change this world!

f60d0964-cd46-4227-b502-de7c564cf603.title: Effigy
f60d0964-cd46-4227-b502-de7c564cf603.text:
Or at least it would if we could ever get it finished. See
those builders?

196a353f-d94b-4bac-a809-323c02cc17c0.title: <player>
196a353f-d94b-4bac-a809-323c02cc17c0.text: They don't seem to be building much.

01bb2650-fde0-4c0b-bbb4-36951cf6682c.title: Effigy
01bb2650-fde0-4c0b-bbb4-36951cf6682c.text:
Exactly. They've gone on strike for some petty reason
about the tower being too weird. I really can't
understand those men.

dd089001-c214-461b-b3c6-7900f9d7875b.title: <player>
dd089001-c214-461b-b3c6-7900f9d7875b.text: Shame. I hope you work it out.

db4ec64d-1ea3-410b-8a5c-5a62f8320121.text:
You do not meet all of the requirements to start
the Tower of Life quest.

4fc12322-02ba-4435-8290-7e7fcca1c0be.title: Effigy
4fc12322-02ba-4435-8290-7e7fcca1c0be.text:
Hey! Maybe you could talk to them? You look pretty
sturdy - maybe you could finish the work?

1a6de831-405d-486a-bc6d-45f0f2894c3a.title: Effigy
1a6de831-405d-486a-bc6d-45f0f2894c3a.text: Come on! This is the chance of a lifetime!

3d55fbce-bebc-4b7c-ae83-dc72fbc4046e.title: <player>
3d55fbce-bebc-4b7c-ae83-dc72fbc4046e.text: Sorry, feeling a bit ill today.

a64f5549-5b39-4de5-8d45-fd15f5a52c89.title: Effigy
a64f5549-5b39-4de5-8d45-fd15f5a52c89.text:
A bit ill? That's a weak excuse for a very feeble
personality.

6bdeb9e7-2280-4651-b98f-754768b3a289.title: Effigy
6bdeb9e7-2280-4651-b98f-754768b3a289.text: That's fantastic! Oh, I'm so pleased.

1b04e33b-8eba-40cb-8807-4b06a729c816.title: <player>
1b04e33b-8eba-40cb-8807-4b06a729c816.text: Calm down. I'm not making any promises.

a5dc1916-e0a7-4965-9ac2-f73f040971c7.title: Effigy
a5dc1916-e0a7-4965-9ac2-f73f040971c7.text: Oh, I have a good feeling about this.

0d3b694b-eceb-4f2a-9206-5cfa2ee772a0.title: Effigy
0d3b694b-eceb-4f2a-9206-5cfa2ee772a0.text:
Right. Go have a word with Bonafido the head builder.
See if you can't get him off his backside to do some
work. Oh, and I'm Effigy by the way.

5c3bd7a5-70e2-4cc7-9266-a677ba2fbb9c.title: <player>
5c3bd7a5-70e2-4cc7-9266-a677ba2fbb9c.text:
Nice to meet you Effigy, I'm <player>. Hold on and
I'll see what I can do!

7f2085b0-cba5-4b8b-ba12-1da9248fff0c.title: <player>
7f2085b0-cba5-4b8b-ba12-1da9248fff0c.text: Hey, Effigy. I've spoken with Bonafido!

66481ba0-ec0e-490d-93b7-a06443caec89.title: <player>
66481ba0-ec0e-490d-93b7-a06443caec89.text:
Well, nothing really, I still need to convince him I'm
worth listening to.

06d0f869-4644-4faa-8c37-99b09c8e9092.title: Effigy
06d0f869-4644-4faa-8c37-99b09c8e9092.text:
Make haste, young adventurer! For the great Tower of
Life awaits no man, and only the impetuous will discover
its virtue!

18d0f3dd-3d61-4502-b22e-d625a15e7f6b.title: <player>
18d0f3dd-3d61-4502-b22e-d625a15e7f6b.text: Why do you talk like that? It's really annoying.

ffa3ee9f-e04d-4f38-8fb3-f4af5c80b7e4.title: <player>
ffa3ee9f-e04d-4f38-8fb3-f4af5c80b7e4.text: What do you want me to do again?

03c07616-9c73-4f24-b018-979c6e6b17f8.title: Effigy
03c07616-9c73-4f24-b018-979c6e6b17f8.text:
Go have a word with Bonafido, the head builder, lying
next to the entrance to the tower. See if you can't get
him off his backside to do some work.

80ed52bb-b8dc-49e2-90e7-7ede1184e018.title: Effigy
80ed52bb-b8dc-49e2-90e7-7ede1184e018.text: Marvellous! So you can bring this tower to life!

48f9c927-ca56-48a5-a033-ab58418a16f7.title: <player>
48f9c927-ca56-48a5-a033-ab58418a16f7.text:
I'm not sure about that, but I'll take a look and see
what I can do.

def796f8-9705-4a2a-89e0-6f8ae78254a6.title: Effigy
def796f8-9705-4a2a-89e0-6f8ae78254a6.text: Oh, what a wondrous person you are!

f501021b-0637-4ba4-bf5b-343ab6c5b2ac.title: <player>
f501021b-0637-4ba4-bf5b-343ab6c5b2ac.text:
Hello again, Effigy. I've had a nose around the tower.
There's a lot of work to do!

3f81ffbf-56bf-40ec-8b69-4cb2d015cd22.title: Effigy
3f81ffbf-56bf-40ec-8b69-4cb2d015cd22.text:
I know, I know. But think of how fantastical it will be
when it is finished!

73b4f02b-921b-4a20-8535-0de363990b8d.title: <player>
73b4f02b-921b-4a20-8535-0de363990b8d.text:
Why fantastical? What are all those pipes and machines
in there? What are you trying to do?

0cb3160e-71d2-41cc-99aa-0080fe75002b.title: Effigy
0cb3160e-71d2-41cc-99aa-0080fe75002b.text: The sun is shining... The birds are singing...

d092677d-54ef-409e-a9f8-968eae32bbb0.title: Effigy
d092677d-54ef-409e-a9f8-968eae32bbb0.text: Hehe. Just fix the tower. You'll soon see.

f78f7adf-9d48-436b-99cd-bcd1b9bd866b.title: <player>
f78f7adf-9d48-436b-99cd-bcd1b9bd866b.text: You'd best pay me well for this.

3d135000-ad3e-4a09-a263-1f0b4ab3124c.title: <player>
3d135000-ad3e-4a09-a263-1f0b4ab3124c.text: Now listen, what does it all do? Why are you-

9eee83de-b506-4c8f-8d12-2220698b238b.title: Effigy
9eee83de-b506-4c8f-8d12-2220698b238b.text: Years of devoted work; it's complete!

8bcf3d31-6cb9-40e8-b7dd-d6feaad9a317.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
8bcf3d31-6cb9-40e8-b7dd-d6feaad9a317.text: At last! Our work is complete!

4d947857-a818-41c8-a4e5-8c486e1cc178.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
4d947857-a818-41c8-a4e5-8c486e1cc178.text: I can almost taste the riches!

87b53fac-e192-4075-b0cd-0779646a26f5.title: Effigy
87b53fac-e192-4075-b0cd-0779646a26f5.text: To the top of the tower, fellow alchemists!

11adfdee-4db6-4179-9548-9e8f7c1aa936.title: <player>
11adfdee-4db6-4179-9548-9e8f7c1aa936.text:
Why does nobody listen?
Best if I follow them, I suppose.

832638e2-c130-4ea1-a962-86fa90406c98.title: Effigy
832638e2-c130-4ea1-a962-86fa90406c98.text:
It is time, my friends! The culmination of our work is
complete!

36714a6f-ff7b-4f87-8904-438c5597f464.title: Effigy
36714a6f-ff7b-4f87-8904-438c5597f464.text:
A great many years of planning and preparation has
brought us here, my fellow alchemists. Now we have...
The Tower of Life! We can already create gold, we
can already transform matter from one thing to

5b216873-b1ef-482d-b562-7b8cb964c7e4.title: Effigy
5b216873-b1ef-482d-b562-7b8cb964c7e4.text:
another, and now we have the ability to create life itself!
We owe much to the power of Guthix, for without the
life essence he left below ground, we would never have
been able to bring this tower alive!

8159ee11-0280-468b-843d-97d330d0fbc6.title: Effigy
8159ee11-0280-468b-843d-97d330d0fbc6.text: It begins! The first day of creation!

13b1bfd6-776c-48cb-a043-920eca7dd62d.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
13b1bfd6-776c-48cb-a043-920eca7dd62d.text: It can talk! A real success.

b0df8302-281b-4341-b391-2f55167ca9bd.title: Homunculus
b0df8302-281b-4341-b391-2f55167ca9bd.text: Where me? Skin burn...arrgh...eyes hurt...let me go!

af1496bd-843b-48a3-9282-3cc5711dffea.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
af1496bd-843b-48a3-9282-3cc5711dffea.text:
Excellent, it can feel! It's self-aware. This is really a
great day.

4bb8739d-2104-4aca-9c04-3f8b2affc919.title: Homunculus
4bb8739d-2104-4aca-9c04-3f8b2affc919.text: Whyeee cage? Argh...please help me! Graaahhh!

09af70dd-1be3-499c-b938-a26e65392439.title: <player>
09af70dd-1be3-499c-b938-a26e65392439.text: This is terrible, you must do something!

33b54422-27ca-4ff7-9448-9d31c0dcb14a.title: Effigy
33b54422-27ca-4ff7-9448-9d31c0dcb14a.text:
Ah, it's our helper. Thank you for fixing the tower; we
will reward you greatly.

74e94d2e-d136-442a-af99-5392a997896f.title: <player>
74e94d2e-d136-442a-af99-5392a997896f.text:
I don't want a reward, just let it go. Can't you see it's
in pain?

c6f9266c-5248-4563-880a-1d45dea6510a.title: Effigy
c6f9266c-5248-4563-880a-1d45dea6510a.text: Don't worry. It has no soul; it has no worth.

9997c244-4eb1-498d-b1f1-4c4715d6bf56.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
9997c244-4eb1-498d-b1f1-4c4715d6bf56.text: Yes, it's just an experiment in alchemy.

61b77a42-c7d0-433f-8fa4-486386746afe.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
61b77a42-c7d0-433f-8fa4-486386746afe.text: The creature must be grateful for his creation.

16cdfe8e-87fa-4c32-9868-eff9b780d315.title: Homunculus
16cdfe8e-87fa-4c32-9868-eff9b780d315.text: You create hurt. Not fair, let me free!

71e7507e-914b-4b5b-8ce2-6a6429e1979c.title: Effigy
71e7507e-914b-4b5b-8ce2-6a6429e1979c.text: Yes, be still and quit your moaning.

b2181b17-a44b-456a-9ba5-b2a78857791c.title: Effigy
b2181b17-a44b-456a-9ba5-b2a78857791c.text:
You should know your place, adventurer. This is no
concern of yours now.

c80ce46b-8cee-4a2e-a3a1-f387b37db1df.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
c80ce46b-8cee-4a2e-a3a1-f387b37db1df.text:
You should be satisfied and leave. Then we can begin
our experiments.

72b07182-36f6-4e46-a499-6db56067004b.title: 'Transmute' The Alchemist
72b07182-36f6-4e46-a499-6db56067004b.text: Get out of the tower before it's too late!

664cb6c6-6a33-495c-8652-7932e37e4c36.title: <player>
664cb6c6-6a33-495c-8652-7932e37e4c36.text:
They've run away. I must go confront those alchemists
downstairs.

379775a7-a2da-4862-bb78-cb637dc9bff1.title: Effigy
379775a7-a2da-4862-bb78-cb637dc9bff1.text:
I know, I know. This is a truly dangerous creation, of
all proportions.

661a9ca3-38cc-42cd-89f8-9dafb920d043.title: <player>
661a9ca3-38cc-42cd-89f8-9dafb920d043.text: I hope you learn from this.

30ccad08-70f3-4d99-bf66-3397f4b5c37c.title: Effigy
30ccad08-70f3-4d99-bf66-3397f4b5c37c.text: I will, I will. Next time we'll use a stronger cage.

12ea7ae5-4c4c-47b8-85b8-0e7c54e6e21d.title: <player>
12ea7ae5-4c4c-47b8-85b8-0e7c54e6e21d.text:
I'll just ignore that. So, what about that Homunculus up
there? You can't just leave it.

848f1294-6482-4baf-b23b-0e12cecf01b9.title: Effigy
848f1294-6482-4baf-b23b-0e12cecf01b9.text: Maybe you could go have a talk with it?

e6aae609-b6ac-4aad-bf5d-fcade11286ae.title: Effigy
e6aae609-b6ac-4aad-bf5d-fcade11286ae.text: Pretty please with a cherry on top?

63eaf0de-ad37-42f3-89c5-bcacfd1d392b.title: Effigy
63eaf0de-ad37-42f3-89c5-bcacfd1d392b.text:
I'll make sure you're compensated. You won't be
forgotten for this!

25a757fc-f2d2-42e9-91dc-d7436aea7a2d.title: <player>
25a757fc-f2d2-42e9-91dc-d7436aea7a2d.text:
Why do I get the feeling I'm doomed to go face that
creature on my own?

4f784912-9efa-446a-8e9d-14833dabbd83.title: Effigy
4f784912-9efa-446a-8e9d-14833dabbd83.text: Good on you! I knew you would help us!

f564d1f7-5228-4885-88b9-44c032cc4904.title: <player>
f564d1f7-5228-4885-88b9-44c032cc4904.text: Oh well. They do say that experience teaches fools.

35ca649e-2455-42af-89ce-c6a5fd52f224.title: Effigy
35ca649e-2455-42af-89ce-c6a5fd52f224.text:
Have you spoken to our wondrously fabulous creation
yet?

50fb17c1-1104-487c-9853-6dd61f18f943.title: <player>
50fb17c1-1104-487c-9853-6dd61f18f943.text:
I haven't spoken to it at all. Give me a chance. And
please stop your overuse of adjectives.

d3a9db92-70a4-4f5a-8391-a3e8ef4d8029.title: Effigy
d3a9db92-70a4-4f5a-8391-a3e8ef4d8029.text:
What a hideously, unforgiveable and insensitive
combination of dialogue to supply to a friend!

67a89f22-3e3f-446a-993c-01214659a7cf.title: <player>
67a89f22-3e3f-446a-993c-01214659a7cf.text:
I swear you'll get a knuckle sandwich sometime soon if
you don't shut up.

769be1b3-790a-44d6-bb6d-a7794c145b27.title: <player>
769be1b3-790a-44d6-bb6d-a7794c145b27.text: Effigy, I need a word with you.

1819c591-bd3f-4172-aba6-8e376dac266a.title: Effigy
1819c591-bd3f-4172-aba6-8e376dac266a.text: You set it free. Oh, please don't hurt me!

a080cef8-8f8a-4509-bbe0-69032ad88c9a.title: Homunculus
a080cef8-8f8a-4509-bbe0-69032ad88c9a.text:
Me not hurt. Now tell. What you plans? What you do
with me?

6e1902cd-93be-4f72-9cc7-a7777d243d87.title: Effigy
6e1902cd-93be-4f72-9cc7-a7777d243d87.text:
Please, we just wanted to experiment. We wanted to
create life. There's a dungeon under the tower. Long
ago we found a strange source of energy that we
believe was left behind by the great Guthix. He used to

f865d37a-a0cc-4406-86ec-3c610f66555d.title: Effigy
f865d37a-a0cc-4406-86ec-3c610f66555d.text:
create life with such ease. We realised we should be able
to use this powerful substance, but we needed to bring
together our magic along with the logical construction of
the builders. It seemed through our experiments that

0159b217-c95c-4bc8-ac2c-0f6eeec88b9a.title: Effigy
0159b217-c95c-4bc8-ac2c-0f6eeec88b9a.text:
even magic needs a certain level of rules and laws to
work.

42677894-c0e8-49b0-a418-28f2c6e0360b.title: Homunculus
42677894-c0e8-49b0-a418-28f2c6e0360b.text: Bad play with. Naughty men. Go! Go, never return!

8a4af2df-897f-4918-8b2f-b4120a54dc33.title: Homunculus
8a4af2df-897f-4918-8b2f-b4120a54dc33.text: Me look dungeon, <player>. Please meet there.
